subject: Tennis
College Athletics
Amateur Athletics
lead_paragraph: The Arkansas women's tennis team will compete in the N.C.A.A. tournament without one of its star players, Aurelija Miseviciute, who was declared ineligible for a year yesterday by the National Collegiate Athletic Association for violating a rule regarding amateurism.
